Resource Profile: FR Core Patient Profile

Official URL: http://hl7.fr/ig/fhir/core/StructureDefinition/fr-core-patient Version: 2.0.0
Draft as of 2023-10-16 Computable Name: FRCorePatientProfile

Profile of the Patient resource for France Profil de la ressource Patient pour l’usage en France
This profile specifies the patient’s identifiers for France. It uses international extensions (birtplace and nationality) and adds specific French extensions Ce profil spécifie les identifiants de patient utilisés en France. Il utilise des extensions internationales (birthplace et nationalité) et ajoute des extensions propres à la France.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: FR Core Appointment Operator Extension, FR Core Appointment Profile, FR Core Encounter Profile, FR Core Medication Administration Inhaled Oxygen Profile... Show 11 more, FR Core Observation Bmi Profile, FR Core Observation Body Height Profile, FR Core Observation Body Temperature Profile, FR Core Observation Body Weight Profile, FR Core Observation Bp Profile, FR Core Observation Head Circum Profile, FR Core Observation Heart Rate Profile, FR Core Oservation Resp Rate Profile, FR Core Observation Oxygen Saturation Profile, FR Core Related Person Profile and FR Core Schedule Profile
